excerpt: Smart seaside fish and seafood restaurant with gallery windows, an outdoor terrace and cocktails.
detail_description: The Oyster Box is a sophisticated seaside restaurant located on the beautiful promenade in St Brelade. It offers stunning views of St Brelades Bay from its luxurious heated terrace. Specializing in oysters, the restaurant serves fresh Jersey rock oysters with various accompaniments such as champagne butter or kenny-herbert sauce with grilled Gruyere cheese. In addition to seafood, the menu features locally sourced meat and fish dishes prepared to order for an authentic Jersey dining experience.
name: Oyster Box
address: St Breladeâ€™s Bay, JE3 8EF, Jersey

detail_description: Located in the heart of St Ouens Bay, El Tico Beach Cantina is a popular spot for both locals and tourists. The restaurant offers stunning views of the beach and a spacious, bright interior with an open kitchen and surf-inspired design. It's known for its extensive menu featuring classic breakfast dishes with innovative twists, as well as comfort-food specials.
name: El Tico
address: Gd Rte des Mielles, Jersey JE3 7FN, Jersey

excerpt: Swish boutique hotel restaurant offering artistic gastronomy in an elegant, art deco-inspired space.
detail_description: Bohemia Bar & Restaurant is a sophisticated establishment within The Club Hotel and Spa, known for its artistic cuisine served in an elegant art deco-inspired setting. With a Michelin Star to its name for 16 years, the restaurant's Head Chef, Callum Graham, showcases seasonal menus featuring exquisite ingredients sourced from Jersey.
name: Bohemia Bar & Restaurant
address: Green St, St Helier, Jersey JE2 4UH, Jersey

detail_description: Ocean Restaurant, situated within The Atlantic Hotel in St Brelades, offers an exceptional dining experience with its modern British cuisine and stunning coastal views. The restaurant's interior design reflects its seaside location, featuring a contemporary nautical ambiance with blues and beiges. With an award-winning reputation and 4 AA Rosettes, the restaurant provides a range of menu options including table d'hote, seasonal a la carte, and tasting menus that can be paired with selected wines.
name: Ocean Restaurant
address: Le, Mont de la Pulente, JE3 8HE, Jersey

detail_description: The Hungry Man, a colorful and iconic burger stand in Rozel Bay, Jersey, has been serving simple yet satisfying dishes since 1947. The menu features bacon rolls, hot dogs, burgers, crab sandwiches, milkshakes, and ice cream that are sure to evoke a sense of nostalgia. Situated next to the bay with stunning views, this eatery is highly recommended for its delicious food despite having a limited menu.
name: The Hungry Man
address: La Brecque du Nord Rozel JE, JE3 5BN, Jersey

detail_description: Samphire is a chic all-day brasserie in St. Helier, Jersey, known for its relaxed yet refined dining experience. The restaurant, now holding a Plate award, offers a convivial approach to showcasing the best of Jersey's local produce. Dishes like tempura Grouville Bay oysters and roasted fillet of Jersey beef highlight the freshness and quality of the ingredients.
name: Samphire
address: 11 Don St, St Helier, Jersey JE2 4TQ, Jersey

detail_description: Located by the shore and the entrance of Gorey village, this gastro pub takes pride in its exceptional service and remarkable cuisine. Each evening, patrons can expect a delectable array of dishes including tempura oysters, scallops, octopus, duck, red mullet, and various flavors of ice cream. In addition to the superb food quality, the restaurant offers a delightful ambiance with both indoor and outdoor dining options.
name: Bass & Lobster Restaurant
address: Gorey Coast Rd, A3, Jersey JE3 6EU, Jersey

detail_description: Sumas Restaurant is located in a charming whitewashed building with a spacious outdoor terrace offering stunning views of Gorey Harbour. The menu features carefully selected local seafood and island-grown vegetables, showcasing the unique flavors of Jersey's produce. As the casual sister restaurant to Longueville Manor, Sumas offers a relaxed seaside dining experience with an emphasis on fresh seafood like local squid and sea bass, as well as options for lamb and chicken.
name: Sumas Restaurant
address: Gorey Pier, Jersey JE3 6ET, Jersey

detail_description: Tassili Restaurant, nestled within The Grand Jersey Hotel and Spa in St Helier, offers a dining experience that is as visually stunning as it is gastronomically delightful. With breathtaking sea views from its large windows, guests can begin their culinary journey with expertly crafted cocktails in the elegant Champagne Lounge.
name: Tassili Restaurant
address: Esplanade, St Helier, Jersey JE2 3QA, Jersey

excerpt: Modern European dishes are served at this chic restaurant with marina views and a heated terrace.
detail_description: Nestled in the vibrant heart of St. Helier, Quayside Bistro & Grill stands as Jersey's largest seafood haven, offering a delightful array of modern European cuisine with an emphasis on fresh fish dishes. Diners can indulge in a variety of oceanic delights such as succulent oysters, crabs, scallops, and sea bass while soaking in stunning marina views from the chic interior or heated terrace.
name: Quayside Bistro & Grill
address: Liberation Square, Liberty Wharf, St Helier, JE2 3NY, Jersey

detail_description: Tides Restaurant & Voyager Lounge Bar is a popular dining spot located in St. Aubin, Jersey. It offers al fresco dining on a large decked terrace, which is favored by both locals and tourists. The menu features classic dishes such as traditional fish & chips and homemade burgers, along with unique offerings like pan-fried scallops in garlic butter and broccoli cream. The restaurant also provides options for those with dietary restrictions or allergies.
name: Tides Restaurant & Voyager Lounge Bar
address: Somerville Hotel, Mont du Boulevard, St Aubin, Jersey JE3 8AD, Jersey

excerpt: Stylish bar/bistro with  a large terrace,and a globally-inspired menu using fresh Jersey produce.
detail_description: The Salty Dog - Cafe, Bar & Bistro is a stylish establishment with a large terrace and a globally-inspired menu that utilizes fresh produce from Jersey. Since 1998, it has been known for its authentically spiced dishes and has built up a great team passionate about good food and service. The restaurant offers an enjoyable dining experience with attractive modern decor, sufficient staff, and efficient service.
name: The Salty Dog - Cafe, Bar & Bistro
address: La Neuve Route, Jersey JE3 8BS, Jersey

detail_description: Mano's Bistro is a fine establishment, particularly for those interested in buffet options. However, it may be best to avoid visiting during weekends if you prefer a quieter and less crowded environment, as the restaurant tends to attract many patrons at that time. The service can be somewhat slow due to the large number of tables needing attention. Nonetheless, the quality of food is commendable and portions are satisfactory. This hidden gem offers an excellent dining experience with friendly and amusing staff members who provide exceptional assistance.
name: Mano's Bistro
address: 5/6 West Centre, Bath St, JE2 4ST, Jersey

detail_description: Located next to Liberation Square in St Helier, Botana is a top spot for dining and drinks, especially during the summer months when outdoor seating is available. The restaurant offers a wide selection of tapas and an extensive variety of wines. Visitors praise the cozy atmosphere and friendly staff, noting that the menu features delicious dishes with incredible flavors. The combination of traditional and innovative cuisine using fresh ingredients adds to the appeal of this standout restaurant in St. Helier.
name: Botana
address: Caledonia Pl, St Helier, Jersey JE2 3QA, Jersey

detail_description: Off The Rails, located in St. Brelade and accessible through the old railway track, is a renowned pizza restaurant in Jersey. It is known for its delectable pizzas made on sourdough crust, which are highly regarded by visitors. The establishment also offers tasty tapas options, making it a versatile dining experience. With a cozy and inviting atmosphere reminiscent of a ski chalet, Off The Rails provides an enjoyable setting for patrons to indulge in their culinary delights.
name: Off The Rails
address: Pt Rte des Mielles, Jersey JE3 8FA, Jersey

detail_description: Nestled on the iconic Portelet Beach, Portelet Bay Cafe offers a unique dining experience with its no-frills menu featuring wood-fired pizzas and locally sourced seafood dishes. Despite occasional service delays on busy nights, the charming atmosphere and stunning views of the bay make it worth the wait. Accessible by foot or boat, this family-run cafe is celebrated for its authentic wood-fired pizzas, freshly caught fish, and seasonal vegetables.
name: Portelet Bay Cafe
address: Portelet Bay, JE3 8PS, Jersey

detail_description: La Taverne, owned by the renowned Miguel De Castro, is a popular restaurant in Jersey. Miguel has gained recognition for his expertise in the culinary industry after working at prestigious establishments like Lily Langtrys, Sea Crest Hotel, and Chateau La Chaire. The restaurant offers a set menu with a variety of options for each course, including steak without any additional charges. Although one customer had their steak overcooked, the rest of the choices were fantastic.
name: La Taverne
address: York Street, St Helier, Jersey JE2 3RQ, Jersey

detail_description: Nestled in the vibrant heart of St. Helier, Cafe Spice is a delightful gem that showcases the rich culinary traditions of Indian and Bangladeshi cuisine. This family-owned restaurant goes beyond the usual offerings, presenting an array of house specialties that truly capture the essence of South Asian flavors.
name: Cafe Spice
address: 53 Kensington Pl, St Helier, Jersey JE2 3PA, Jersey

This family-run establishment, managed by the Le Boutillier family for five generations, boasts an impressive working farm with around 400 cows and features its own butchery and creamery. name: The Potato Shack
address: Woodlands Farm, Rue de Maupertuis, JE2 3HG, Jersey

name: Awabi
address: 63 Halkett Pl, St Helier, Jersey JE2 4WG, Jersey
